NAME: unmute
DESCRIPTION: Unmute an user on the server.
OPTIONS_NOTIFY_DESCRIPTION: Whether to notify the user of the unmute.
OPTIONS_VISIBLE_DESCRIPTION: Whether to show the unmute in the channel.
MUTED: **An user has been unmuted on the server.**
PERMISSIONS: The user you want to unmute either have a higher role than you or the bot doesn't have the permissions to unmute them.
NOT_MEMBER: The user is not a member of the server.
